The stable version can be checked out using the following command:
	svn co http://svn.atheme.org/atheme/branches/release-2.2 atheme-stable

The development version has moved to Mercurial, it can be checked out using
the following command:
	hg clone http://hg.atheme.org/atheme atheme-devel

Atheme's SVN repository can be browsed over the internet at the 
following address:
	http://viewsvn.atheme.org/
